narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Don't take it unless you have to for the Art requirement. Or, I've heard the class is better with other teachers.
This is a course where you will try out every aspect of art making that foes not involve traditional media.
Most people taking this course are planning to be art majors, so you have to take it, but I would also recommend it for somebody interested in trying out a variety of media.
If you're an Art major, it's not really an option is it?

This is a rigorous art class with some academic backbone. Expect to work a bit harder (as in shorter timespan) in the middle of the course. I heard this is the best instructor to take this course with. I really enjoyed the structure and would definitely recommend the course.
